@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Rejected
Rejected --> Processing : approve
Processing --> Archived : reject
Processing : entry / log student
Archived --> Approved : update
Approved --> Closed : reject
Closed --> OnHold : approve
Closed : entry / log student
Closed --> Rejected : revert
OnHold --> [*]
@enduml